OL,3,C'I feel like a second-class citizen':
OL,4,CPlea for help from disabled people
OL,6,FA man living with a disability in
OL,7,FJersey says that the rising cost of
OL,8,Fliving is continuing to put pressure
OL,9,Fon his family's finances.
OL,11,FA recent UK report found that, on
OL,12,Faverage, it costs disabled households
OL,13,Fmore than #1,000 a month to have the
OL,14,Fsame living standard as an able-bodied
OL,15,Fhome.
OL,17,FLocal charities believe this figure
OL,18,Fcould be even higher for those living
OL,19,Fin the Channel Islands.
