OL,3,C'I feel like a second-class citizen':
OL,4,CPlea for help from disabled people
OL,6,F"To coin a phrase, you're a second-
OL,7,Fclass citizen. I love Jersey, I've
OL,8,Fbeen here 36 years, I was born here, I
OL,9,Flove the island, but it does sometimes
OL,10,Ffeel like I'm being pushed out because
OL,11,Fof my disability.
OL,13,F"It really impacts you detrimentally.
OL,14,FIt can even get to the point where
OL,15,Feven getting out of bed and you're
OL,16,Fworried about financial stuff - for
OL,17,Fme, it can cause my body to just go
OL,18,Frigid and not be able to move.
