OL,3,C'I feel like a second-class citizen':
OL,4,CPlea for help from disabled people
OL,6,F"If you can't use the bus, then
OL,7,Fthere's the extra cost of using a taxi
OL,8,Fif you can't drive. But if you do
OL,9,Fdrive, your fuel costs are high. Fuel
OL,10,Fcosts at the moment are high for
OL,11,Feveryone, but if you rely on a car,
OL,12,Fit's detrimental.
OL,14,FCharities say they have seen more
OL,15,Fislanders coming to them for help and
OL,16,Fsupport.
OL,18,FSuzanne Day from Enable Jersey
OL,19,Fexplains: "My understanding is that
OL,20,Fthose subsidies aren't there.
