OL,3,C'I feel like a second-class citizen':
OL,4,CPlea for help from disabled people
OL,6,F"When people are looking at their
OL,7,Fenergy bills, they are stuck with
OL,8,Fthem. We do know that certain parishes
OL,9,Fwill help people, and charities help
OL,10,Fand do an amazing job.
OL,12,F"There are some limited benefits from
OL,13,Fthe government, but they are very
OL,14,Flimited - not everyone is able to
OL,15,Fapply, so we know that this impacts
OL,16,Fmore and more of our community."
