OL,3,C'I feel like a second-class citizen':
OL,4,CPlea for help from disabled people
OL,6,FIn response, Jersey's Social Security
OL,7,FMinister, Deputy Lyndsay Feltham,
OL,8,Fsays: "We do recognise that people
OL,9,Fwith a disability are likely to have
OL,10,Fmore costs than those without a
OL,11,Fdisability.
OL,13,F"That's recognised through increased
OL,14,Fcomponents in income support and also
OL,15,Four long-term incapacity allowance.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/8
