OL,3,C'I feel like a second-class citizen':
OL,4,CPlea for help from disabled people
OL,6,F"We do have our cold-weather bonus,
OL,7,Fwhich will be available to a number of
OL,8,Fpeople. I'm always keen to hear from
OL,9,Fpeople about their experiences so we
OL,10,Fcan look to improve things in the
OL,11,Ffuture."
OL,13,FThis problem exists in Guernsey too -
OL,14,Fthe Guernsey Blind Association says
OL,15,Fthat even though there is extra help,
OL,16,Fthe number of islanders with
OL,17,Fdisabilities needing support is at an
OL,18,Funprecedented level.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/8
