OL,3,C'I feel like a second-class citizen':
OL,4,CPlea for help from disabled people
OL,6,FChantelle Tucker, Vision Support
OL,7,FServices Officer for the charity,
OL,8,Fexplains: "The assistance has
OL,9,Fincreased dramatically over the last
OL,10,Ffew years.
OL,12,F"But I think people don't necessarily
OL,13,Funderstand that some of the equipment
OL,14,Fthey need to go about their day-to-day
OL,15,Flife and work is essential, not
OL,16,Foptional; it can be very expensive."
